steps.name: open the url on Chrome web browser
click the all outer cells on the grid, do not click the inner cells
the pop-box should open with a display message
enter a valid number in boundary to start again with a new size of grid

elements.name: Player clicks all the cells on the grid

steps.name: open the url on Chrome web browser
click the all outer and the inner cells on the grid
the pop-box should NOT open with a display message

elements.name: Player enters a number out of boundary

steps.name: open the url on Chrome web browser
click the all outer cells on the grid, do not click the inner cells
the pop-box should open with a display message
enter a number out of boundary
the NOTIFY message ""Not a good size!"" should appear in the pop up box
